    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/223a18-2/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=603258941572383477&sectionId=603258941656400629)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","label":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","default":"Discover why 40,000+ women using Collagen Infused Mouth Tape &nbsp;To Snatch Their Jawline and Hydrate Lips While They Sleep"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","label":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","default":"<p>By Eleanor Brooks | London, UK<br>December 7, 2025</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggy5Uy9f896_text","label":"ggy5Uy9f896_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I’ll be honest—I used to scroll right past the mouth taping trend. It looked uncomfortable. But then I realized it’s actually a&nbsp;<strong>3-in-1 powerhouse: it fixes your sleep, sharpens your jawline, and prevents lip wrinkles all at once.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfwG-WQa7r_text","label":"ggfwG-WQa7r_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">That’s when I found this brand, unlike harsh medical tapes, they created a&nbsp;<strong>Hydrolyzed Collagen&nbsp;</strong>version that actively hydrates your skin while you wear it.&nbsp;</span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I’m usually skeptical of viral products, but I decided to put this to the test for a week.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-b7-Ufnz_text","label":"ggj-b7-Ufnz_text","default":"Here are the 7 reasons why I’ve actually stuck with it:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","label":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","default":"1. It’s A \"Nighttime Retainer\" For Your Face Structure."},{"type":"html","id":"ggvDN5djePx_text","label":"ggvDN5djePx_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(244, 204, 204, 0);color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">When your mouth hangs open at night, gravity drags your facial muscles downward for 8 hours straight. This creates what experts call&nbsp;<strong>\"Mouth Breather Face\"</strong>: a longer, droopier face shape.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(244, 204, 204, 0);color:#000000;font-size:16px;\"><strong>Nifora&nbsp;</strong>prevents this by keeping the jaw lifted and closed. This forces Nasal Breathing, which&nbsp;<strong>naturally rests your tongue on the roof of your mouth (a technique called \"Mewing\")</strong>. The result?&nbsp;<strong>High cheekbones and a snatched jawline, all achieved while you sleep.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNzvrSfCrV_text","label":"ggNzvrSfCrV_text","default":"2. It’s Collagen Skincare, Not Just Tape"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxwUzin72S_text","label":"ggxwUzin72S_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Most mouth tapes are just sticky plastic or paper that can irritate your skin.&nbsp;<strong>Nifora’s strips are infused with Hydrolyzed Collagen</strong>, meaning the particles are small enough to actually sink in while you sleep.&nbsp;<strong>It works like a targeted sheet mask that hydrates the area for 8 hours straight.&nbsp;</strong>So instead of just holding my mouth shut, I’m waking up with that delicate skin feeling softer and plumper.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","label":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","default":"3. It Lowers \"Cortisol Face\" (Morning Puffiness)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","label":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(244,204,204,0);color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Experts have found that mouth breathing keeps your body in a&nbsp;<strong>state of micro-stress (Fight or Flight)</strong> all night long. This spikes your Cortisol levels, which causes your body to hold onto water, leading to that round \"Moon Face\" look in the morning.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(244,204,204,0);color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">Nifora forces your body to switch into deep restorative&nbsp;<strong>Nasal Breathing</strong>. This allows your body to naturally drain excess fluid and inflammation while you sleep. The result?&nbsp;<strong>You wake up with a slim, depuffed face and defined cheekbones</strong>, without needing to ice roll for 20 minutes.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","label":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","default":"4. It’s The Ultimate 3-in-1 Multitasker&nbsp;"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","label":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">I realized this isn't just a sleep aid;<strong> it’s doing three jobs at once</strong>. First, my jawline is getting visible again!&nbsp;<strong>It improves my face posture by keeping my jaw in the right position all night.&nbsp;</strong>Second, while it’s holding that structure,&nbsp;<strong>the collagen is actively treating my skin</strong>. And third, because I’m finally getting deep, restorative sleep,<strong> I wake up feeling genuinely healthy and energized</strong>. It’s rare to find one product that tackles posture, skincare, and health simultaneously.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHIzq54zz__text","label":"ggHIzq54zz__text","default":"5. It Doesn't Hurt To Take Off"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text","label":"ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">My biggest worry was that it would hurt to peel off in the morning. Because of the collagen infusion,&nbsp;<strong>the adhesive is actually very gentle</strong>. It stays on all night without issues, but in the morning,&nbsp;<strong>it peels off easily without pulling my skin or leaving red marks.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOkzpODfF8_text","label":"ggOkzpODfF8_text","default":"6. The Quality of My Sleep Has Completely Changed"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3BajX3jAe_text","label":"gg3BajX3jAe_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">This is the most important part. I learned that mouth breathing actually keeps your body in a state of stress (\"fight or flight\") all night, preventing you from fully shutting down. By forcing nasal breathing,<strong> this tape increases oxygen intake and signals your nervous system to relax.</strong> It pushes you into deep REM sleep much faster. I’m not just waking up less groggy<strong>; I’m waking up with lower cortisol levels and actual energy. This is where the real body repair and \"beauty sleep\" happens.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTCZJLSmNN_text","label":"ggTCZJLSmNN_text","default":"7. You Can Try It Risk-Free"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOGc25WEdF_text","label":"ggOGc25WEdF_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:16px;\">It’s always annoying to buy a new product and hate it.&nbsp;<strong>Nifora offers a risk-free trial, so if you find it uncomfortable or don't see a difference, you aren't stuck with it</strong>. For me, the better sleep and smoother skin are worth it.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggL99cbnlZo_text","label":"ggL99cbnlZo_text","default":"<p><strong>UPDATE:</strong> The Collagen Mouth Tape is currently in stock, but inventory is moving fast. Check the link below to see if it's available.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUMmUh3HgV_label","label":"ggUMmUh3HgV_label","default":"<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>"}],
